      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and UTS from ASTM E8 tensile tests on production-lot coupons (N=5). Geometry from CMM measurements of production screws. Monte Carlo uncertainty propagation with 1000 samples performed; 95th percentile QOI uncertainty is 6.3%."
