      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario physics and geometry sufficiently similar to intended use conditions to support extrapolation of credibility evidence.",
      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 test configuration replicates the biomechanical loading environment of lumbar spinal fixation. Non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw geometry tested matches the intended clinical device. Validation scenario relevance confirmed by biomechanical subject matter expert review."
